# Automatic Email Sender Django Project

Automatically send event-related emails to employees using Django.

## Table of Contents
- [Project Overview](#project-overview)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Testing](#testing)



## Project Overview
This project aims to automate the process of sending event-related emails, such as birthdays and work anniversaries, to employees. It utilizes Django, a Python web framework, for building the backend. The project involves models to represent employees, events, email templates, and email sending logs. It also includes views for sending emails Manually and a cron job for scheduling the email sending process.


